description: EventProducerS: Table recording events from various network elements (CUUP, DU, CUCP) within specific cells, including timestamps, location, and identification information.  Columns: dateTime (event timestamp), Area_Name (geographic area), CellId (cell tower identifier), Id2 (redundant cell identifier), Id3 (likely a generic identifier), Id4 (network element type), vsDataType (data type identifier), vsDataFormatVersion (data format version), EventProducerS.eventProducerSId (network element ID), EventProducerS.streamDestinationPort (port number for event stream).
